        {
            "title": "伊朗戰事推高油價 布蘭特期油衝破119美元全球股市受挫",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">受伊朗戰事影響，國際油價周四再度急升，進一步收緊全球經濟，並拖累全球股市大幅下挫。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">國際基準布蘭特期油（Brent crude）早上曾短暫升穿每桶119美元，其後回落至112.70美元，較前一日仍上升5%。美國基準原油每桶則上漲1.4%至96.78美元。此前，伊朗為回應以色列對其重要天然氣田的襲擊，加劇了對波斯灣（Persian Gulf）周邊油氣設施的攻擊。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"紐約證券交易所交易大堂。AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/1abeddf7c4bf19d1dc96b3f23c1de402_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street_28660.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"紐約證券交易所交易大堂。AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/644x392/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/1abeddf7c4bf19d1dc96b3f23c1de402_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street_28660.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">紐約證券交易所交易大堂。AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"紐約證券交易所交易大堂。AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/1abeddf7c4bf19d1dc96b3f23c1de402_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street_80005.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"紐約證券交易所交易大堂。AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/644x392/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/1abeddf7c4bf19d1dc96b3f23c1de402_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street_80005.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">紐約證券交易所交易大堂。AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"紐約證券交易所交易大堂。 AP